    <h1>Best Free PDF Table Extractors</h1>
    <p>The best free PDF table extractor depends on your document type and privacy needs.</p>
    <h2>Online table extractors</h2>
    <p>Online tools are convenient for quick, non-sensitive files. Look for clear file deletion policies and download formats like XLSX and CSV.</p>
    <h2>Desktop and open-source tools</h2>
    <p>Tools such as Tabula are strong for technical users who want local processing, especially for text-based PDFs.</p>
    <h2>OCR tools</h2>
    <p>For scanned PDFs, OCR is required before table extraction. OCR is more expensive and should be evaluated separately from simple text-based extraction.</p>
